modName: Newmiller succubus outfit for Sevenbase Bombshell BBP
summary: Newmiller succubus outfit converted for Sevenbase body type
descriptionHtml:
Newmiller succubus outfit for Sevenbase Bombshell

Required :

Sevenbase Bombshell body
BBP Skeleton

Installing :

1) Download original mod (suit + boots) - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33893/?

2) Download this and overwrite

3) Enjoy
